text: Vaceuchelus ludiviniae is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Chilodontidae. ==Description== The size of the shell varies between 2.7 mm and 4.5 mm. ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off the Philippines. ==References== ==External links== * ludiviniae Category:Gastropods described in 2006
title: Vaceuchelus ludiviniae
